  "detailed_description": "<h1>♥♥ ADD IN WISHLIST!! ♥♥</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660500/extras/db45c24a63becfffe2c3a84918dfd545.webp?t=1768963460\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660500/extras/db45c24a63becfffe2c3a84918dfd545.poster.avif?t=1768963460\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=64 /></picture></span><br>Main character is a working professional with a history of multiple failed blind dates.<br>One day, after the usual disappointing end to yet another blind date, he decided to release his soul with video games.<br>He never expected to be transported to isekai such suddenly,. Just as he was about to be attacked by strange creatures,<br>A strangely dressed young girl appeared before him..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660500/extras/fdffeb919ede98a9a191d71f98f0df64.webp?t=1768963460\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660500/extras/fdffeb919ede98a9a191d71f98f0df64.poster.avif?t=1768963460\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=64 /></picture></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>This game is heavily inspired by『Vampire Survivors』<br></li><li>Various skills can be upgraded, helping you defeat 20+ kinds of monsters!<br></li><li>You can also challenge leaderboard after clearing all stages.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660500/extras/726684f39994b5ae17a0b44fd5bf9c49.poster.avif?t=1768963460\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660500/extras/726684f39994b5ae17a0b44fd5bf9c49.webm?t=1768963460\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2660500/extras/726684f39994b5ae17a0b44fd5bf9c49.mp4?t=1768963460\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>   ",
